<div class="content">
  <h2>About CAAL</h2>

  <p>
    The Clinical Anaesthetists Association of Lesotho (CAAL) is a professional body
    representing anaesthesia providers in Lesotho.
  </p>

  <h3>Our Mission</h3>
  <p>
    To promote safe anaesthesia practice, education, and professional development
    in Lesotho.
  </p>

  <h3>Our Vision</h3>
  <p>
    To be a leading organization in advancing anaesthesia care and patient safety.
  </p>

  <h3>Our Objectives</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Promote education and training</li>
    <li>Advocate for patient safety</li>
    <li>Support research and innovation</li>
    <li>Collaborate with international bodies</li>
  </ul>
</div>

